full_meeting_data.title: Meeting with Merdan Durdyev
full_meeting_data.description: Merdan proposed a meeting on June 25 at 09:00 AM.

full_email_data.body:
Good! Let's do it on June 25, 09:00 AM

On Sat, Jun 21, 2025 at 5:53 PM <sales@zemzen.org> wrote:

> Hi there,
>
> It was a pleasure speaking with you earlier today!
>
> As promised, here’s a proposal tailored for Le Croissant. We
> understand your commitment to offering the Logan community exceptional
> artisan breads, pastries, and delicious lunch options, including your
> well-regarded vegan choices. Our aim is to help you stand out in the
> competitive market.
>
> Please take a look at the attached proposal for a detailed overview of
> how we can help Le Croissant achieve its goals.
>
> I’m also excited to share a preview of the demo website, created just
> for you! You can view it here:
>
> https://6000-firebase-studio-1750537617452.cluster-2xfkbshw5rfguuk5qupw267afs.cloudworkstations.dev/
>
> To move forward, what time works best for you for a quick chat next
> week to discuss? Or if you are happy with the prototype, just reply to
> this email, and we can send you the contract.
>
> Looking forward to your response!
>
> Best regards,
>
> Lexi
> ZemZen
> sales@zemzen.org
full_email_data.subject: Re: Follow-up on Our Recent Call - Proposal for Le Croissant in Logan
